Code.Terraform:
```hcl
resource "google_container_node_pool" "<example_resource_name>" {
  name     = "<example_resource_name>"
  cluster  = "<example_resource_name>"
  location = "<example_resource_name>"

  node_config {
    service_account = "<example_resource_name>@<example_resource_id>.iam.gserviceaccount.com" # critical: use a custom SA, not the Compute Engine default
  }
}
```
